item.description: Namaste! I am presently prepping up for starting my PhD in Electrical Enginnering department at Arizona State University. Here, I will be working with Prof. Angelia Nedich and Prof. Anna Scaglione on Large Scale Optimization. Previously, I was holding the position of Systems Engineer at Netradyne. I was working on using sensor information from Mobile devices/IMU chips to draw out statistics on the general driving behavior of an individual to develop better driver safety features.
